  "text": "Pontin also appears to act as an anti-apoptotic factor. Indeed, a dominant-negative mutant of Pontin, devoid of ATPase activity, potentiates the apoptotic activity of c-myc and of E2F1 [CITATION_1] . We found that, similar to Reptin, the knock-down of Pontin in HCC cells led to spontaneous apoptosis 1 .",
